00:10.208 --> 00:13.832
ANARCHIST FROM THE COLONY

00:13.916 --> 00:18.416
<i>All the characters in this film
are based on actual historical figures</i>

00:20.540 --> 00:24.708
<i>Tokyo, 1923</i>

00:30.624 --> 00:34.040
<i>I'm only a damn dog.</i>

00:35.916 --> 00:38.372
<i>Barking at the sky.</i>

00:38.956 --> 00:41.956
<i>Barking at the moon.</i>

00:43.332 --> 00:48.124
<i>I'm only a worthless damn dog.</i>

00:53.540 --> 00:54.832
Here we are.

