we'll all end up dead.

29:36.092 --> 29:39.880
I can't believe we just walked
into the police station.

29:39.964 --> 29:42.216
They say we poisoned the wells?

29:42.800 --> 29:44.340
Then, let's poison them!

29:44.880 --> 29:47.840
We set fire? Then, let us set fire!

29:48.464 --> 29:52.592
We're not against the Japanese people.

30:00.924 --> 30:04.671
Let me get inside! The
vigilantes are here.

30:04.672 --> 30:07.380
They're killing every
single Korean they see.

30:07.716 --> 30:08.592
What's police doing?

30:08.632 --> 30:10.092
They're ignoring us.

30:10.380 --> 30:12.840
Please, open up.

30:13.924 --> 30:16.508
Please help!

30:24.340 --> 30:26.424
All of you.

30:27.464 --> 30:29.340
You're Koreans, right?

30:30.380 --> 30:31.464
Am I right?

30:33.840 --> 30:36.008
Fifteen bucks, fifty cents.

30:37.132 --> 30:38.592
Say it.

30:40.172 --> 30:41.508
Hey, you.

30:48.592 --> 30:49.840
Say it.

30:53.092 --> 30:55.172
Fuck off! You fucking asshole.

30:56.880 --> 31:00.592
Yeah, I'm fucking Korean,
you motherfucker.

31:02.672 --> 31:04.840
Stop and get out now.

31:05.216 --> 31:07.423
Why are you protecting dirty Koreans?

31:07.424 --> 31:09.800
Get out, right now!

31:10.132 --> 31:12.355
We helped you get rid of the barbarians.

31:12.380 --> 31:17.256
It's for the good of our country.

31:26.464 --> 31:28.508
Things are getting serious.

31:28.800 --> 31:33.964
Thousands of Koreans have been arrested.

31:34.300 --> 31:36.507
We have no more facilities to keep them.

31:36.508 --> 31:40.880
What did I say? It's okay to kill them.

31:41.716 --> 31:45.048
The vigilantes have already
begun to slaughter them.

31:45.380 --> 31:49.508
Massacre is spreading to
Gunma and Saitama areas.

31:49.840 --> 31:52.840
<i>Koreans slaughtered in Gunma and Saitama.</i>

31:58.964 --> 32:02.300
This shouldn't be in papers.
Stop them run this headline!

32:02.424 --> 32:03.424
Yes, sir!

32:05.800 --> 32:08.716
<i>430 Koreans Massacred in Kanto</i>

32:09.258 --> 32:11.386
Is this number accurate?

32:11.712 --> 32:14.668
That's the official number now.

32:14.716 --> 32:18.172
The number's reaching
almost 6,000 nationwide.

32:22.256 --> 32:25.672
Six... thousand?

32:27.548 --> 32:29.839
It's quite a lot of number
within three days

32:29.840 --> 32:31.756
after the earthquake.

32:44.340 --> 32:47.508
Pick one from those locked in the station.

32:47.592 --> 32:49.048
Which one?

32:51.292 --> 32:53.123
One who is a hero to Koreans,

32:53.124 --> 32:56.208
